text: Henri de La Tour d'Auvergne, Viscount of Turenne (1611-1675) was a French general, serving the Kingdom of France from 1630 until his death on 27 July 1675 during the Battle of Salzbach. title: Henri de la Tour d'Auvergne, Vicomte de Turenne
